{"parse":{"title":"The British Legion (1860)","pageid":53237352,"revid":856998343,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"summary\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Expedition of the Thousand</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#DCDCDC;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;\">Part of the wars of <a href=\"/wiki/Italian_Unification\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Italian Unification\">Italian Unification</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;line-height:1.5em;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Garibaldian_volunteers..jpeg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Garibaldian volunteers..jpeg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Garibaldian_volunteers..jpeg/220px-Garibaldian_volunteers..jpeg\" width=\"220\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Garibaldian_volunteers..jpeg/330px-Garibaldian_volunteers..jpeg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Garibaldian_volunteers..jpeg/440px-Garibaldian_volunteers..jpeg 2x\" data-file-width=\"760\" data-file-height=\"709\" /></a><br />The British Legion in Southern Italy</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><table style=\"width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0\"><tbody><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Date</th><td>1860\u20131861</td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Location</th><td><span class=\"location\"><a href=\"/wiki/Southern_Italy\" title=\"Southern Italy\">Southern Italy</a></span></td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Result</th><td>\nUnification victory;<br />Collapse of the <a href=\"/wiki/Kingdom_of_the_Two_Sicilies\" title=\"Kingdom of the Two Sicilies\">Two Sicilies</a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-siz